title: Another young golfer makes his mark
text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle Emiliano Grillo sinks a birdie putt to defeat Kevin Na on the second playoff hole to win the Frys.com Open at the Silverado Resort on Sun. October 18, 2015. Emiliano Grillo sinks a birdie putt to defeat Kevin Na on the...
Emiliano Grillo, an utterly anonymous 23-year-old from Argentina, found a novel way to attract attention Saturday at the Frys.com Open. He mistakenly thought the green was clear at No. 17, a short par-4, and smacked his tee shot into the distance.
